500 户，实际居住人口约 3.6 万人。 今年 4 月，上海康城第五届业主委员会发布《关于上海康城物业服务质量问题的沟通整改函》。 其中提到，为维护小区广大业主的权益，上海康城第五届业主委员向深圳碧桂园盛孚物业服务有限公司上海分公司发出关于上海康城物业服务质量问题的沟通整改函。根据整改函，康城业主对物业公司服务质量的不满主要涉及工程维修问题、保洁问题、保安问题、绿化问题、客服问题、维保维修费用问题等方面。 上海最大居民小区宣布：炒掉物业"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1cc9b516e05dce6ad444b78040709b19_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "131 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665977826"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItsDvoLiR89tJEAMaCTExMDI3Mjk0MCCL1tS2BjAAOEFACHIJNjY1OTc3ODI2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1725275008.743752", "card_id": "Q_665698262", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价殷桃、王骁主演的电视剧《凡人歌》?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4da98eddf505e8deca0b19ce6be9514c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "111 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665698262"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItsDvoLiR89tJEAMaCTExMDIxMDQ1OSDAnMW2BjAAOCpACXIJNjY1Njk4MjYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1725275008.744056", "card_id": "Q_665783011", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "看完《阿甘正传》，有什么难忘的台词？"}, "excerpt_area": {"te